headline: Dover to Present at the UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference 2025
summary: Dover Corporation (NYSE: DOV) announced that its President and Chief Executive Officer, Richard J. Tobin, will speak at the UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference in West Palm Beach, Florida, on Tuesday, December 2, 2025, at 11:20 am ET.
